@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### Attendance: Get Students (Admin/Warden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/students?course=&branch=&gender=&category=&roomNumber=
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}

### Attendance: Take Attendance
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/take
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-01-01",
  "records": [
    { "studentId": "{{STUDENT_ID}}", "status": "Present" }
  ]
}

### Attendance: Get Attendance For Date
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/date?date=2025-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}

### Attendance: Get Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/range?start=2025-01-01&end=2025-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}

### Attendance: Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/stats?start=2025-01-01&end=2025-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}

### Attendance: Update
PUT {{baseUrl}}/attendance/update
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{STUDENT_ID}}",
  "date": "2025-01-01",
  "status": "Absent"
}

### Attendance: Delete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/attendance/{{STUDENT_ID}}/2025-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_OR_WARDEN_TOKEN}}


